Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89485,91529}Like this you won't depend on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97702,100121}What? Didn't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100121,101289}I have homeworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103041,104417}My God! My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110506,111883}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111883,113468}You want milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114260,117430}I apologize for walking all this distance, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118723,120350}You know, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120350,122727}I can't give you milk today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:10.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129734,130610}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142288,143206}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143206,144957}There's no milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:25.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144957,145750}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146417,148753}I thought it would be okay\Nwhen I relied on Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150713,152340}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152340,153383}A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153466,154592}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:36.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154592,156761}The milk has been ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158137,160139}But that huge cow…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160640,164602}The milk placed in the soup would taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164602,166688}We have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166688,168147}What? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168815,170066}To Sandy's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175530,177657}What will he do with his homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183246,184747}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184747,186874}The cow is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186874,187500}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188042,190753}I thought she was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:11.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190753,191754}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191754,192964}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:16.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192964,196718}It can give milk when it eats well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196718,197677}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197635,199011}But?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199178,202014}Mm, no longer give any drop of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203641,205518}Don't it give milk when it eats well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207603,208938}This…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208938,211816}A veal tries to suck without caring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:35.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211816,215528}It can't drink other than its milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215528,218030}Mother's milk is its favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249562,251814}We have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252565,255985}Ah…Dad, aren't you thinking the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255985,258863}It's better to be more kind…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258863,260865}There's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260865,262992}You have to reach any convincing result!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262992,266329}Dear, if you shout aloud\Nour children will wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:32.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267413,272001}Ah… children are children…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272001,276130}That cow is Sandy's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276130,279967}She also learned how to milk cow's milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:40.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279967,280760}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280760,283179}Sandy is very happy with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283179,285348}It's enough! Stop this talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286307,288434}I also worked hard for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288935,290812}No, that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290812,294065}So you have to find some way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294065,296609}Dad, are you weak in front of these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296609,297819}It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297819,299779}The cow is not like pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299779,302281}If it does not help, we won't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302281,304742}If we don't get milk,\Nwe will not benefit from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305576,307453}Eh…So…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308204,310873}I'll take it to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311207,312208}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:16.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312208,316128}It's better to do that when Sandy\Ngoes to school… okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319549,322718}What to do? What to do? What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359046,360339}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360798,362300}Yes, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362300,363968}But, is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363968,364594}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364594,366804}I heard of the presence of a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366804,368306}What, a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377273,378608}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:19.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378608,379567}xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379567,381986}The cow of my kind daughter has been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381986,384780}I don't forgive the cause of this concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386407,389076}How can you be sure there was a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389076,392747}There was a lock on the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392747,394540}What do you think of opening it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:39.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394540,399253}Or do you think the cow\Nopened the lock and ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399253,402006}No, I can't even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402965,404592}Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:49.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404592,409305}Next time I will find a cow thief no matter\Nif I search inside your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:55.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409722,415311}But if there is no thief you will put\Nyourself in an awkward position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415311,417271}This happened to me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417271,419774}He stole from us two cows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419774,421651}We must arrest him and punish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421651,424528}Is it good to let this bad person go free?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425696,427949}It's not easy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:12.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427949,432161}Well you found it! You found\Nany evidence and told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432161,433996}I won't cooperate with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435206,436999}Well, his saying is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436999,438542}He doesn't have any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438542,440670}We can't help him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440670,441337}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441837,444382}Sandy, that's a problem, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445132,446884}I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448928,450972}This is better for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450972,452098}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:36.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452098,456852}I'm worried about what he's thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456852,459730}What a subject he wants to sell my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459730,462149}Eh?What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463275,464402}- Oh…\N- Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:52.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467571,472410}Henry VII, took the subject of religiosity\Nin the country more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:56.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472410,476914}So he firmly believed that the war would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:01.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476914,481377}Henry VII entered northern\Nand southern Scotland…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486173,487425}Damn…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490386,493681}I don't care if no one cooperates with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508279,509363}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509363,512992}If you want any help from us, let us know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512992,514076}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515661,517121}Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517121,518831}Do you really want to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519749,520624}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520624,522543}The weather is very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522543,524420}Maybe I can't help you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524420,527089}Don't you want to tell you a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527089,528174}A secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529508,530551}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530551,531594}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532470,534972}Well I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534972,536557}It's a very important secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563209,565252}John! Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566587,567880}Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567880,570758}Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572676,574762}Sandy, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574762,576555}You are not Sandy we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576555,579058}Die if you tell! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579058,580601}I-I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580601,582770}Yes.Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588192,591946}Now I'll tell you about\Nmy most important secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591946,592738}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602540,603541}It's the voice of the cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604166,605334}Could it be that cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605334,607586}Wait! Listen to me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607586,610047}But the thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611549,613092}The thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615177,616095}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616095,617054}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634363,637992}You also expected this will end very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637992,638701}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639326,642121}But I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644582,646542}What are you going to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647126,649003}I never thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650212,653883}I also can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653883,657636}It's better to tell your father, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657636,658721}I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658721,660890}My father can never help
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660890,663225}so he didn't find any reason to feed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664059,666729}We can't do anything without\Nfinding a suitable idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666729,668063}Let's think about it ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668063,669732}So we find a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670316,672067}What if we find no good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672067,673611}We will find a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673611,676071}We will definitely find a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676071,677239}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677239,677948}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678866,680534}Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683704,685372}The weather is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687541,689501}It's okay to stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689501,692046}I have to be a little happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695216,696425}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696425,699803}Oh…Will the milk come out if we pull it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699803,702223}Yes, it must happen but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702223,705017}We have done this several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705017,706477}Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706477,707811}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724411,725329}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725329,726705}Hear its voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726705,729041}Yeah, there are some people with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730584,731543}Okay!
Comment: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:14.25,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:734255,734255}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738008,739051}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740135,742554}This is the biggest proof\Nof the thief's existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742554,745057}Bansen will take us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747685,749520}But that's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749520,750896}This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750896,752147}Let's do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752147,753857}What? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753857,755734}Aren't you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755734,759571}Oh, I was drunk a bit at that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760155,761198}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761198,763409}It might be something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763409,764952}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764952,767162}This is our chance to take the cow away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767162,768038}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773335,774670}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776130,777047}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777047,778799}There is work to be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780759,784305}I want you to go with Bansen and all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785306,787308}Is there any objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787725,788934}No other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788934,790311}Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793897,795566}Sandy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795566,797860}If we don't hurry up,\Npeople will arrive before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798193,799320}Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799320,802072}We must catch the thief before he escapes us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:24.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802072,804074}Is the thief really there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804074,806368}For some reason the situation has reversed…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806535,809496}Hey, all of you hasten more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809496,811498}Colin! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817463,819298}Moo, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819298,821508}I must take you somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821508,823469}And now hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826221,827222}Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836357,838442}Is this the right way? Haven't you mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838442,839902}Yeah, maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843781,844656}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845699,848327}It's not good to stay here, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852289,854208}What's the matter, Moo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854208,856085}She won't move…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861298,863300}Well, listen, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863300,865010}Let's do it in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:25.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865010,865886}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866303,867721}There's something here which seems lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867721,868889}Is it with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869598,871266}No, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872351,874103}This is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874103,876730}Yesterday I dropped it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876730,879858}How does a drunk like you forget\Nthe most important thing he has?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881151,884822}This is not the time to laugh!\NEveryone shouldn't take eyes off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884822,886240}Is it near?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886240,887366}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888283,891078}From that way? Or where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891078,892871}No, but from there…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893580,894623}But there…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894623,895374}In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895833,898836}It seems that Lassie has found something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898836,900379}Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901588,903048}Well done, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903048,904216}In here! In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906927,908637}Everyone goes in a different way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909263,911140}John did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911140,912891}This is our chance, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913058,915894}Let's go from here, Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927322,929158}Don't do that, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929158,932077}We have to drag them to another road!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938250,939168}Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939168,940461}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940461,942921}If we stay here, my father will find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947801,949761}Moo, do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949761,952431}What will happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952890,956435}As I expected, she can't\Nunderstand our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956435,958937}Is not so, is that right, Moo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:15:59.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958937,959938}Moo's baby…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965819,967821}Hey, if we go this way…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967821,969406}- Eh?\N- John, wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:09.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969406,969990}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970866,973368}There is no way out in this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973368,974077}Eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981502,983378}Don't know if the thief\Nwent this way on a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983378,986298}But the cow and its baby\Ncan't cross this river.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988175,991637}Isn't it better to go back\Nto the previous place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992554,993555}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:34.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994139,994932}Eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007194,1008195}In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009029,1010447}All of you follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014117,1016870}Don't go back to this way, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017246,1018413}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018413,1020999}That road was blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025629,1027965}Lassie, don't go this way…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:11.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031260,1031969}In here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039268,1041853}Oh? What is that? This place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041853,1043855}Amazing…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044606,1046441}Mountain grapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:35.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050779,1055242}This is the best mountain grapes\Nwe can make wine from!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:41.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056451,1061248}Abandon the cows and milk, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062082,1063500}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063500,1064751}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072968,1074886}Follow us, follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074886,1076805}It was better to do this from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082894,1084313}Stop it, Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084313,1085772}We have to hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086148,1087232}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:10.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090110,1090819}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091820,1092696}Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092696,1094156}Uncle, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095282,1096241}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107502,1110589}Do you understand what you've done wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111882,1115302}Moo… Moo… I wanted to save them…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115302,1117262}I don't want you to sell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118096,1119806}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:43.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119806,1123477}Do you think I would prefer to sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124019,1126021}Because of your help for Moo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126021,1128482}I faced more difficulty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128982,1130359}You have to understand that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131151,1132861}I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132861,1135447}If you don't want to sell it, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135447,1136907}Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137866,1139743}Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139743,1141703}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147042,1148585}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155425,1158637}Uncle, can't you help Moo in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158637,1160972}You say I help her? If I could,\NI have done that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160972,1164393}You too! You did reckless things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168271,1171566}Moo's baby is about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171566,1172901}If left next to Moo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172901,1176488}it can never drink cow's milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176863,1179741}But, maybe there is some way…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179741,1181993}Well that's a lot… too much…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205976,1207060}Hello, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:11.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208103,1211690}Has not changed yet…\NHer milk has not yet come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216236,1217404}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217404,1218864}You are also worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:25.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222993,1225495}Well, you can't stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227247,1228290}Sandy…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232419,1233462}Sandy…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:38.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237966,1238967}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242596,1243972}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243972,1245098}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245098,1247392}Moo! The milk came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250604,1253482}What is the matter? Why did everyone rush so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254357,1255776}I don't believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267078,1268330}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268330,1271124}I was looking hard for these flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271124,1273293}When Sandy's father was born
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273293,1276004}we made her eat them until\Nher condition improved one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276630,1278048}Is this a popular remedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278048,1279090}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:19.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279090,1279966}Moo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282552,1285055}You, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287098,1288683}Isn't it wonderful, Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289476,1291269}No, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291269,1294147}I can't do anything except milking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294147,1295941}You leave this job to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296650,1297901}Silly…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299569,1300695}Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301863,1303532}I'm sorry…
